title: Teriyaki Chicken Crisp nutritional specifications
statement: The Teriyaki Chicken Crisp contains 1g carbs, less than 1g sugar, 13g protein, and is dairy-free and gluten-free.

citations.quote: Low Carb/Keto Friendly (1G Carbs) ✓ Zero Sugar (<1G) ✓ High Protein (13G) ✓ Dairy Free ✓ Gluten Free
